                  <div style="width:100%;" class="nsp_art">
                   <div style="padding:2px 4px 2px 4px">
                    <h4 class="nsp_header tleft fnone">
                     <a title="Riva Uddingston’s Weekend of Indoor Success" href="/2011/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=620:riva-uddingstons-weekend-of-indoor-success&catid=1:latest-news&Itemid=2">
                      Riva Uddingston’s Weekend of Indoor Success
                     </a>
                    </h4>
                    <p class="nsp_info  tleft fnone">
                     24 Dec 2015
                    </p>
                    <a title="Riva Uddingston’s Weekend of Indoor Success" class=" tleft fleft" href="/2011/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=620:riva-uddingstons-weekend-of-indoor-success&catid=1:latest-news&Itemid=2">
                     <img style="width:160px;height:120px;margin:3px 5px 3px 5px;" title="Riva Uddingston’s Weekend of Indoor Success" alt="Riva Uddingston’s Weekend of Indoor Success" src="/2011/images/stories/images/news/2015/2015122401.jpg" class="nsp_image tleft fleft" />
                    </a>
                    <p class="nsp_text tleft fleft">
                    </p>
                    <p>
                     On Saturday, Riva Uddingston Men’s Indoor First Team ended the first half of the indoor season on a high, finishing third place in Indoor National League One.  This is the first time in Uddingston Hockey Club’s history that a team has challenged in National League Division one.  This sets the team up nicely for the second half of the season...
                     <a href="/2011/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=620:riva-uddingstons-weekend-of-indoor-success&catid=1:latest-news&Itemid=2" class="nsp_readmore inline">
                      Read more
                     </a>
                    </p>
                    <p class="nsp_info  tleft fnone">
                    </p>
                   </div>
                  </div>
                  <div style="width:100%;" class="nsp_art">
                   <div style="padding:2px 4px 2px 4px">
                    <h4 class="nsp_header tleft fnone">
                     <a title="Palazzo Uddingston Youth Satellite Club of 2015" href="/2011/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=619:palazzo-uddingston-youth-satellite-club-of-2015&catid=1:latest-news&Itemid=2">
                      Palazzo Uddingston Youth Satellite Club of 2015
                     </a>
                    </h4>
                    <p class="nsp_info  tleft fnone">
                     18 Dec 2015
                    </p>
                    <a title="Palazzo Uddingston Youth Satellite Club of 2015" class=" tleft fleft" href="/2011/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=619:palazzo-uddingston-youth-satellite-club-of-2015&catid=1:latest-news&Itemid=2">
                     <img style="width:160px;height:120px;margin:3px 5px 3px 5px;" title="Palazzo Uddingston Youth Satellite Club of 2015" alt="Palazzo Uddingston Youth Satellite Club of 2015" src="/2011/images/stories/images/news/2015/2015121801.jpg" class="nsp_image tleft fleft" />
                    </a>
                    <p class="nsp_text tleft fleft">
                    </p>
                    <p>
                     “The last Palazzo Uddingston Youth Satellite Club of 2015 took place at EastBank Academy on Wednesday evening.  The club has been running for almost a year where children from Eastbank academy and 5 local primary schools are invited to attend an after-school transition club open to P5-S2 pupils.  As part of Palazzo Uddingston’s in-school programme all schools receive 5-6 week...
                     <a href="/2011/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=619:palazzo-uddingston-youth-satellite-club-of-2015&catid=1:latest-news&Itemid=2" class="nsp_readmore inline">
                      Read more
                     </a>
                    </p>
                    <p class="nsp_info  tleft fnone">
                    </p>
                   </div>
                  </div>
                  <div style="width:100%;" class="nsp_art">
                   <div style="padding:2px 4px 2px 4px">
                    <h4 class="nsp_header tleft fnone">
                     <a title="Uddingston Hockey Club hosted hockey festivals to celebrate the hard work of children" href="/2011/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=618:uddingston-hockey-club-hosted-hockey-festivals-to-celebrate-the-hard-work-of-p6-children&catid=1:latest-news&Itemid=2">
                      Uddingston Hockey Club hosted hockey festivals to celebrate the hard work of children
                     </a>
                    </h4>
                    <p class="nsp_info  tleft fnone">
                     09 Dec 2015
                    </p>
                    <a title="Uddingston Hockey Club hosted hockey festivals to celebrate the hard work of children" class=" tleft fleft" href="/2011/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=618:uddingston-hockey-club-hosted-hockey-festivals-to-celebrate-the-hard-work-of-p6-children&catid=1:latest-news&Itemid=2">
                     <img style="width:160px;height:120px;margin:3px 5px 3px 5px;" title="Uddingston Hockey Club hosted hockey festivals to celebrate the hard work of children" alt="Uddingston Hockey Club hosted hockey festivals to celebrate the hard work of children" src="/2011/images/stories/images/news/2015/2015120901.jpg" class="nsp_image tleft fleft" />
                    </a>
                    <p class="nsp_text tleft fleft">
                    </p>
                    <p>
                     Uddingston Hockey Club Hosted hockey festivals over two days last week to celebrate the hard work of the P6 children who had been practicing hockey, as part of the club’s in school programme, during their PE timetable.  Eleven schools took part in either a morning or afternoon session, where teams played in continuous friendly games in a ¼ of the...
