                      550 kids add hockey festival to their experiences of playing popular sport
                     </a>
                    </h4>
                    <p class="nsp_info  tleft fnone">
                     08 Dec 2015
                    </p>
                    <a title="550 kids add hockey festival to their experiences of playing popular sport" class=" tleft fleft" href="/2011/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=617:550-kids-add-hockey-festival-to-their-experiences-of-playing-popular-sport&catid=1:latest-news&Itemid=2">
                     <img style="width:160px;height:120px;margin:3px 5px 3px 5px;" title="550 kids add hockey festival to their experiences of playing popular sport" alt="550 kids add hockey festival to their experiences of playing popular sport" src="/2011/images/stories/images/news/2015/2015120801.jpg" class="nsp_image tleft fleft" />
                    </a>
                    <p class="nsp_text tleft fleft">
                    </p>
                    <p>
                     Uddingston Cricket and Sports Club was the venue on two days last week for an exciting hockey festival featuring around 550 P6 youngsters. The pupils loved playing friendly round robin matches on the new purpose built, water-based astroturf pitch,with contests taking place last Tuesday and Thursday between 9.30 and 11.30am and noon and 2pm. Event organiser Tom Hyndman, a fulltime...
